quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  7,196,Yaqeenan mera madadgar Allah Taalaa hai jiss ney yeh kitab nazil farmaee aur woh nek bandon ki madad kerta hai
  7,197,Aur tum jin logon ki Allah ko chor ker ibadat kertay ho woh tumhari kuch madad nahi ker saktay aur na woh apni madad ker saktay hain
  7,198,Aur agar inn ko koi baat batlaney ko pukaro to iss ko na sunen aur inn ko aap dekhtay hain kay goya woh aap ko dekh rahey hain aur woh kuch bhi nahi dekhtay
  7,199,Aap dar guzar ko ikhtiyar keren nek kaam ki taleem den aur jahilon say aik kinara hojayen
  7,200,Aur agar aap ko koi waswasa shetan ki taraf say aaney lagay to Allah ki panah maang liya kijiye bila shuba woh khoob sunnay wala khoob jannay wala hai
  7,201,Yaqeenan jo log khud taras hain jab unn ko koi khatra shetan ki taraf say aajata hai to woh yaad mein lag jatay hain so yakayak unn ki aankhen khul jati hain
  7,202,Aur jo shetan kay tabey hain woh inn ko gumrahi mein kheenchay ley jatay hain pus woh baaz nahi aatay
  7,203,Aur jab aap koi moajza inn kay samney zahir nahi kertay to woh log kehtay hain kay aap yeh moajza kiyon na laye? Aap farma dijiye! Kay mein uss ka ittabaa kerta hun jo mujh per meray rab ki taraf say hukum bheja gaya hai yeh goya bohr si daleelen hain tumharay rab ki taraf say aur hodayat aur rehmat hai unn logon kay liye jo eman rakhtay hain
  7,204,Aur jab quran parha jaya keray to iss ki taraf kaan laga diya kero aur khamosh raha kero umeed hai kay tum per rehmat ho
  7,205,Aur aey shaks! Apney rab ki yaad kiya ker apney dil mein aajzi kay sath aur khof kay sath aur zor ki aawaz ki nisbat kum aawaz kay sath subha aur shaam aur ehal-e-ghaflat mein say mat hona
  7,206,Yaqeenan jo teray rab kay nazdeek hain woh uss ki ibadat say takabbur nahi kertay aur uss ki paki biyan kertay hain aur uss ko sajda kertay hain